Kuthiwa isitshudeni siphaphame ekuseni singasaligqokile iphenti. Okhulumela amaphoyisa, uCaptain Xoli Mbele uthe: “Isitshudeni sithe besisephathini. Indoda ibe isisinikeza ingilazi yewayini. Sithe silale ubusuku bonke saze savuka ekuseni ngo-4.30.” Kusolwa ukuthi kungenzeka ukuthi kukhona ebikufakile esiphuzweni sesitshudeni. Kuthiwa sivuke sabiza itekisi, sabona lapho ukuthi iphenti laso likhunyuliwe ngesikhathi silele sabikela onogada. Udaba lube selubikwa emaphoyiseni kwase kuboshwa indoda. UCaptain Mbele uthe amaphoyisa asaphenya. Indoda izovela enkantolo kuleli sonto. Okhulumela iWits, uNksz Buhle Zuma, uthe: “Besingakabikelwa ngokudlwengulwa kwesitshudeni kodwa sisathinte ababhekelele ukuvikeleka kwezitshudeni. Sicele ukuthi basebenzisane namaphoyisa ukuze kutholakale lesi sitshudeni bese siyasizwa.” Uphiko olululeka izitshudeni ngokomqondo kulesi sikhungo kuthiwa lulindele ukusiza.